Programming Language Pragmatics, Third Edition

by Michael L. Scott 

Morgan Kaufmann Publishers © 2009 (941 pages) Citation

ISBN:9780123745149

Featuring a rigorous but accessible teaching style, this text provides a worthy tour of the theory and practice of how programming languages are run on today's computers.
